Observability:
- Add KSM metrics from the strimzi operator https://github.com/strimzi/strimzi-kafka-operator/blob/main/examples/metrics/kube-state-metrics/configmap.yaml
- Add PrometheusRule template with alerts (broker down, replication lag, high latency, disk space) from https://github.com/strimzi/strimzi-kafka-operator/blob/main/examples/metrics/kube-state-metrics
- Write runbooks for each critical alert

Testing (apptest-framework on WCs):
- Basic deployment + integration test: install app, deploy Kafka CR, verify pods ready, verify metrics endpoint
- Upgrade/rollback test: bump chart version, verify topic/message persistence
- Chaos test: delete operator pod, verify leader election and recovery

Documentation:
- Auth/authz examples: KafkaUser, SASL/SCRAM, mTLS, cert-manager integration
- Backup/DR docs: MirrorMaker2 for cross-cluster replication, PVC snapshot approach (Velero), retention policy config
- Operational runbook: broker down, scale brokers, rebalance with Cruise Control
- Troubleshooting guide: OOM, disk full, ISR shrinkage, common misconfigurations
